  {"id":"fx.voice-01","type":"example_fixture","query":"先别直接写这场父女争吵戏，先给我一份 voice style guide，让女儿像一个真正在压抑愤怒的人，而不是作者在替她抒情。","intent":"design","medium":"feature_film","stage":"scene","output":"voice_style_guide","constraints":{"voice_target":"suppressed_anger","experiential_depth":"embodied","language_register":"contemporary_realist"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.voice-style-calibration","protocol_id":"wp.voice-style-guide","rubric_id":"rb.voice-style-guide"},"key_checks":["guide should distinguish surface wording from lived pressure","should describe what makes the voice feel alive rather than writerly"]},
  {"id":"fx.voice-02","type":"example_fixture","query":"我要续写一个既有 IP 的角色对白，先做 voice style guide，帮我守住角色世界观和说话习惯，不要写成另一个人。","intent":"adapt","medium":"episodic","stage":"dialogue","output":"voice_style_guide","constraints":{"ip_continuity":"strict","voice_target":"character_continuity","reference_depth":"focus_pack"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.voice-style-calibration","protocol_id":"wp.voice-style-guide","rubric_id":"rb.voice-style-guide"},"key_checks":["guide should define continuity anchors","should identify drift risks that break IP identity"]},
  {"id":"fx.voice-03","type":"example_fixture","query":"给这条高端护肤品牌片做一个 voice style guide，我要高级但不能假、能卖但不能像硬广口播。","intent":"design","medium":"branded_film","stage":"scene","output":"voice_style_guide","constraints":{"voice_target":"aspirational_but_grounded","language_register":"premium_brand","business_model":"brand_lift"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.voice-style-calibration","protocol_id":"wp.voice-style-guide","rubric_id":"rb.voice-style-guide"},"key_checks":["guide should balance persuasion and lived texture","should state what would make the language feel fake-premium"]},
  {"id":"fx.voice-04","type":"example_fixture","query":"这场互动悬疑里的嫌疑人台词总像功能 NPC，先做 voice style guide，让他像一个会遮掩、会自保的活人。","intent":"diagnose","medium":"branching_interactive","stage":"dialogue","output":"voice_style_guide","constraints":{"voice_target":"deflective_self_protection","experiential_depth":"high","participation_mode":"player_interrogation"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.voice-style-calibration","protocol_id":"wp.voice-style-guide","rubric_id":"rb.voice-style-guide"},"key_checks":["guide should connect voice to interaction pressure","should define failure signs of functional-NPC dialogue"]},

  {"id":"fx.visual-01","type":"example_fixture","query":"先别写成稿，给这场家庭晚餐戏做一个 visual language pack，用日语镜头语言锁住留白、停顿和木漏れ日这层气质。","intent":"design","medium":"feature_film","stage":"scene","output":"visual_language_pack","constraints":{"visual_vocab_locale":"ja","aesthetic_register":"pause_plus_transience"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.visual-language","protocol_id":"wp.visual-language-pack","rubric_id":"rb.visual-language-pack"},"key_checks":["pack should be task-bounded rather than dictionary-like","should include misuse or drift warnings"]},
