  {"id":"fx.cast-01","type":"example_fixture","query":"这部原创犯罪长片先别写剧情，先给我一份 expert subagent cast。我要功能型专家、反例节点，以及一层偏 prestige moral collision 的参考 persona。","intent":"design","medium":"feature_film","stage":"premise","output":"expert_subagent_cast","constraints":{"team_mode":"feature_dev_pod","subagent_family":"mixed","persona_policy":"calibrated_reference","selection_strategy":"minimum_viable_cast"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.expert-subagent-casting","protocol_id":"wp.expert-subagent-cast","rubric_id":"rb.expert-subagent-cast"},"key_checks":["cast should separate functional roles from process nodes","persona should stay governed rather than becoming direct mimicry"]},
  {"id":"fx.cast-02","type":"example_fixture","query":"给这个流媒体悬疑剧做一个 expert subagent cast，像 writers' room 一样，但别一上来把所有专家都塞进场。","intent":"discover","medium":"episodic","stage":"structure","output":"expert_subagent_cast","constraints":{"team_mode":"showrunner_room","selection_strategy":"staged_expansion","parallelism_budget":"3_lanes"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.expert-subagent-casting","protocol_id":"wp.expert-subagent-cast","rubric_id":"rb.expert-subagent-cast"},"key_checks":["cast should include trim order","should name convergence owner or handoff path"]},
  {"id":"fx.dispatch-01","type":"example_fixture","query":"这部动画长片已经有 story trust 的 team mode 了，现在给我一个 subagent dispatch plan，重点是 story lane 和 visual lane 怎么双轨调度、怎么 sync。","intent":"design","medium":"animation","stage":"outline","output":"subagent_dispatch_plan","constraints":{"team_mode":"animation_story_trust","dispatch_topology":"dual_track_story_visual","convergence_owner":"director_or_story_lead","context_budget":"bounded"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.subagent-dispatch-design","protocol_id":"wp.subagent-dispatch-plan","rubric_id":"rb.subagent-dispatch-plan"},"key_checks":["plan should define dual-track sync points","should keep lane budgets bounded"]},
