  {"id":"fx.surface-01","type":"example_fixture","query":"这部原创电影项目别先写 outline，先给我一个 project surface map，把 source of truth、runtime state 和 review surface 分开。","intent":"design","medium":"feature_film","stage":"premise","output":"project_surface_map","constraints":{"project_horizon":"long_running_feature","phase_focus":"planning","truth_surface_policy":"human_editable_core","runtime_surface_policy":"derived_runtime_only"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.project-surface-design","protocol_id":"wp.project-surface-map","rubric_id":"rb.project-surface-map"},"key_checks":["map should distinguish editable truth from derived runtime","review surfaces should be named"]},
  {"id":"fx.surface-02","type":"example_fixture","query":"这个短剧项目要经历策划、分集、自检、合规和导出，先做一个 project surface map，把 phase entrypoint 和 export surface 设计清楚。","intent":"discover","medium":"short_drama","stage":"structure","output":"project_surface_map","constraints":{"project_horizon":"production_line_short_drama","phase_focus":"review_and_export","packet_strategy":"inspectable_command_packets","traceability_level":"review_ready"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.project-surface-design","protocol_id":"wp.project-surface-map","rubric_id":"rb.project-surface-map"},"key_checks":["map should define phase entrypoints","export surface should not be mixed with planning truth"]},
  {"id":"fx.surface-03","type":"example_fixture","query":"给这个品牌 campaign 的多 agent 写作流程做一份 project surface map，我要 canonical packet、handoff surface 和 tool-facing export 都清楚。","intent":"adapt","medium":"branded_film","stage":"adaptation","output":"project_surface_map","constraints":{"team_mode":"brand_content_studio","phase_focus":"handoff_and_delivery","packet_strategy":"canonical_packet_bundle","edit_policy":"source_only_human_edits"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.project-surface-design","protocol_id":"wp.project-surface-map","rubric_id":"rb.project-surface-map"},"key_checks":["canonical packet should be inspectable","tool-facing export should be distinct from editable source"]},

  {"id":"fx.checkpoint-01","type":"example_fixture","query":"这部长片写到中段了，我要停两天。先给我一个 story memory checkpoint，别让我下次还得把全部大纲和场景都重读一遍。","intent":"design","medium":"feature_film","stage":"outline","output":"story_memory_checkpoint","constraints":{"phase_focus":"resume_after_pause","continuity_invariants":"character_goal_and_seed_payoff","traceability_level":"review_ready","context_budget":"bounded"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.story-memory-checkpoint","protocol_id":"wp.story-memory-checkpoint","rubric_id":"rb.story-memory-checkpoint"},"key_checks":["checkpoint should compress state instead of retelling the whole story","should include a next safe entrypoint"]},
  {"id":"fx.checkpoint-02","type":"example_fixture","query":"这个八集悬疑剧 room 开完第三集后，先做一个 story memory checkpoint，方便下一轮 break 不用重新加载整份 season 包。","intent":"design","medium":"episodic","stage":"structure","output":"story_memory_checkpoint","constraints":{"phase_focus":"room_handoff","continuity_invariants":"season_arc_and_open_threads","traceability_level":"audit_ready","context_budget":"small"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.story-memory-checkpoint","protocol_id":"wp.story-memory-checkpoint","rubric_id":"rb.story-memory-checkpoint"},"key_checks":["checkpoint should distinguish episode closure from season propulsion","should retain unresolved lines and arc-budget status"]},

  {"id":"fx.research-01","type":"example_fixture","query":"我不是要立刻写页稿，先从故事发动机、观众理解、协作开发、学习训练和档案角度，给我一份‘如何创作剧本’的 research background map。","intent":"discover","medium":"feature_film","stage":"ideation","output":"research_background_map","constraints":{"research_scope":"screenplay_creation_foundations","reference_depth":"survey_pack","route_certainty":"low"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.research-background","protocol_id":"wp.research-background-map","rubric_id":"rb.research-background-map"},"key_checks":["map should decompose the question into multiple lenses","callable atoms and next routes should be explicit"]},
  {"id":"fx.research-02","type":"example_fixture","query":"我在设计编剧 Agent Skill，不是要你写剧本。先给我一份 research background map，重点看观众认知、改稿反馈和开发流程。","intent":"design","medium":"episodic","stage":"rewrite","output":"research_background_map","constraints":{"research_scope":"viewer_cognition_and_development_workflow","reference_depth":"teaching_pack","route_certainty":"medium"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.research-background","protocol_id":"wp.research-background-map","rubric_id":"rb.research-background-map"},"key_checks":["map should distinguish stable findings from local workflow practice","bundle should stay research-oriented instead of collapsing into rewrite advice"]},

  {"id":"fx.quality-01","type":"example_fixture","query":"这场电影 scene draft 先别改，先给我一份 quality gate report，做 full audit，重点看它到底是不是场景功能没立住。","intent":"diagnose","medium":"feature_film","stage":"scene","output":"quality_gate_report","constraints":{"target_contract":"scene_draft","audit_scope":"full_audit","check_depth":"development_room"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.quality-gating","protocol_id":"wp.quality-gate-report","rubric_id":"rb.quality-gate-report"},"key_checks":["report should lock target contract before judging quality","should separate hard fails from weighted weaknesses"]},
  {"id":"fx.quality-02","type":"example_fixture","query":"这条 15 秒短视频广告脚本上线前先做一个 quality gate report，我要 preflight，不要只给 rewrite 意见。","intent":"design","medium":"shortform_video","stage":"scene","output":"quality_gate_report","constraints":{"target_contract":"commercial_script","audit_scope":"full_audit","check_depth":"preflight","acceptance_bar":"launch_ready"},"expected_route":{"skill_id":"skill.quality-gating","protocol_id":"wp.quality-gate-report","rubric_id":"rb.quality-gate-report"},"key_checks":["report should include operational or delivery risk","should not collapse into generic copy notes"]},
